reviewText:
This is one of my favorites in the series as well. Most of the ladies here are pretty hot in my book. WELL worth having!
The top 3 for me, are Julie Cialini, Traci Adell, Elisa Bridges.
** PLAYMATES ARE ~
~ VICTORIA ZDROK
~ KELLY GALLAGHER
~ CINDY BROWN
~ RHONDA ADAMS
~ JULIE CIALINI (Playmate of the Year 1995)
~ TRACI ADELL (one of the hottest brunettes I have ever seen! Those eyes!)
~ MELISSA HOLIDAY
~ MARIA CHECA
